'''Lauren Selmon Roberts'''   ni umukinnyi wa firime ndetse akaba na producer ukomoka muri [[amerika]] . Ni umuyobozi wa ''Rainbow Town'', documentaire yibanze ku mfubyi muri [[Liberiya|Liberiya yatewe]] n'intambara. <ref>https://www.fernsehserien.de/lauren-selmon-roberts/filmografie</ref> <ref>https://mubi.com/cast/lauren-selmon-roberts</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Ni umukobwa wa Kathryn na Dewey Selmon wa Norman, Oklahoma . Yarangije impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu itangazamakuru ryamamaza muri kaminuza ya Leta ya California, Fresno muri Gicurasi 2005. Nyuma yaho, yahawe impamyabumenyi ihanitse y’ubuhanzi bwiza yakuye muri College of Mass Communication and Media Arts of Southern Illinois University Carbondale . <ref>https://news.siu.edu/2010/02/020210par10017.php</ref>

Igihe yari afite imyaka 14, yatangiye gukoresha kamera ya videwo. Roberts yakoze amashusho ye ya mbere, yinjira mubucuruzi bwa WNBA afite imyaka 15. Muri kiriya gihe, yatangiye gukina imirimo myinshi mwishuri nko gutanga raporo, kubyara, kurasa no gutunganya. Amaze kurangiza amashuri, yakoraga kumiyoboro yamakuru. <ref name="fatales">http://www.filmfatales.org/directors/laurenselmonroberts</ref>

Hagati aho, yagiye muri Afurika y'Iburengerazuba gushaka documentaire. Nyuma yimyaka ibiri akorana nimpfubyi zintambara & abahoze ari abasirikari babana muri Liberiya, yahisemo gukora documentaire ye yambere yuzuye, ''Umujyi wa Rainbow Town'' muri 2010. Yabaye kandi umukinnyi wa sinema akaba n'umwanditsi wa documentaire. Iyi filime irazenguruka inkuru yukuri yumugore warokoye ubuzima bwimfubyi zintambara zirenga 250 mugihe cyintambara yabenegihugu. Nyuma yo gushimwa cyane, iyi filime yanahawe igihembo n’umuyobozi wa Guild of America. Nyuma yaje kwerekanwa muri New York Fashion Week, mu nzu ndangamurage ya Tolerance International Festival Festival ndetse nandi maserukiramuco ya firime mpuzamahanga. <ref name="fatales" />

Nyuma yo gutsinda kwa filime, yinjiye nka producer muri NBCUniversal uruganda rukora uruganda, 'Peacock Productions'.  Kuva mu 2011, yakoraga nka producer wungirije, producer wungirije hamwe na producer nyobozi kuri serivise zitandukanye za tereviziyo, umwihariko wa TV hamwe na documentaire.

